{
  "texts": [
    "In addition to this, the study applied image enhancement and noise removal methods to the histopathology samples to complete the preprocessing phase.",
    "Once the input is preprocessed, the framework pipes the inputs to their respective feature extraction and buffering phase.",
    "This ready the features for application of binary optimization method which serves to blind-out features that are not computed to have little relevance to the classification process.",
    "Blind-out features are eliminated leaving the relevant for to be fed to the classifier, while the probability distribution of the batch samples is passed as input to the fusion layer.",
    "In the following subsections, the approach of the fusion layers and the BEOSA method on this layer and the CNN feature extraction phase, are discussed."
  ]
}